strings: <voice_0x01000D58><se_low>King Trode: Are we not already in possession of the Venus' tear? Why didn't you just give it to her?

<voice_0x01000D59><se_low>Yangus: Nah! You don't get it, do ya Grandad!?
We've gotta make 'er think we're goin' to
the cave for 'er, see. We gotta play it cool.
<voice_0x01000D5A><se_low>Yangus: Otherwise she's gonna think we've done nuffin' special. She won't 'ave no gratistude!
